    "OptionDescription": {
      "Namespace": "",
      "Key": "D4394B2F43C0307CA970B88921B6867C",
      "SourceString": "Determines if personal timers can be saved and loaded. On load the timer will return to the state it was saved as. If set to SAVE AND PAUSE, the current time will be recorded and the timer will pause. If set to SAVE AND CONTINUE, the current time will be recorded and timer will continue running.",
      "LocalizedString": "Determines if personal timers can be saved and loaded. On load the timer will return to the state it was saved as. If set to SAVE AND PAUSE, the current time will be recorded and the timer will pause. If set to SAVE AND CONTINUE, the current time will be recorded and timer will continue running."
